node.text:
The harder the battle, the sweeter the victory 👑 

For the @pho3nixife Sub8 Project, I will face many battles.
The battle with history,
The battle with my limits,
And the battle with my rival - @nicolaspirigofficial 

This is going to be a whole new push on what’s possible but I am ready to take on the battle and prove what I can do 🥇

#DefyTheImpossible  #Pho3nix  #Sub7Sub8  #Triathlon 
🎬 @mana.studios  @orbitalstud.io |

node.text:
Smiling because it’s nearly race day! 🏁

Want some more insight into what it took to get here? Hit the link in my bio 🔗 to follow the ups and downs of the journey to the start line! 

📸: @hollycharlesphotography_ 

#raceday #ironmanworldchampionship #triathlete #gamefaceon #livetorace #workhard #livingthedream #motivated #determined #athletemotivation #raceweek #womeninsport #dreamteam #livetoinspire #dontwishforitworkforit #anythingispossible #letsgetit #gohard #smilesformiles #dreambelieveachieve #givesyouwings #becube #ironmantri #teamcharlesbarclay

node.text:
‘The older you get the better you get, unless you are a banana…’😅🍌 
Turning 28 today & feeling so grateful to live this life; chasing my dreams & getting stronger year on year!💪🏻
Also what a place to spend my birthday🥳 
📸: @hollycharlesphotography_ 
#birthdaygirl #itsmybirthday #strongwomen #girlpower #workoutwednesday #girlswholift #livetoinspire #trichicks #swimbikerun #triathlontraining #womeninsport #spottheknot #knowledgeisprogress #TeamCharlesBarclay

node.text:
London 🇬🇧 >>> Utah 🇺🇸 

Just over a week since we made our epic road trip to Cedar City, Utah! 

We documented the whole thing so now you can follow our long journey across the world and see what Team Charles-Barclay get up to in the Wild West 🤠 

🔗 Hit the link in my bio to watch now! 
🎥: @hollycharlesphotography_

node.text:
Do you want to win a 4 night stay at my home away from home…? 🏠🏝

There’s no better place to get a great day of training done - all the facilities you could possibly need & the perfect location for long rides and trail runs!

To enter all you need to do is:

🏝Like this post 
🏝Follow me! @lucycharles93 
🏝Follow @clublasanta 
🏝Tag the friend you would share your trip with in the comments!

🏝Giveaway closes 11.09.2021 at 11.59pm (BST) 

📸: @hollycharlesphotography_ 

*Must be over 18 years old to enter. 4-night stay for 2 people in a Comfort 1 apartment in Club La Santa Lanzarote. Stay window: May, June and September 2022. Subject to availability. Board and travel expenses not included. This promotion is in no way sponsored, administered or associated with Instagram.
